Josh Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josh_Taylor 0 Josh Taylor (born September 25, 1943) is an American actor. He is best known for playing the roles of Chris Kositchek (he originated in 1977) and Roman Brady on the American dramatic serial Days of Our Lives, Jack McKay on the teen drama Beverly Hills, 90210 and as Michael Hogan, the father figure on NBC's situation comedy The Hogan Family.
